-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/taylor-swift-shania-twain-2019-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/taylor-swift-shania-twain-2019-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/taylor-swift-shania-twain-2019-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩</a>分享了对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>的新赞扬——看看下面唐恩怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/shania-twain-interview-queen-of-me-georgia-glastonbury-3405932">仙妮亚·唐恩：“我最自豪的可能是没有放弃我的声音”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://hauteliving.com/2024/04/why-shania-twain-is-in-her-making-the-most-of-life-era//747517/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《高级生活》</em></a>的新封面人物简介中，仙妮亚·唐恩谈到了她在接受与生俱来的才华方面的麻烦：“我不会说我为自己所做的任何事情感到自豪。对我来说，骄傲这个词并不是一个很好的词，因为我认为如果你生来就有创造性的天赋，你就不能将其归功于你；你只能因开发它们而获得荣誉。我想说的是，我感到自豪的是，我有勇气去冒险，我可以如此勤奋和奉献。” </p><figure id="attachment_3584976" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3584976" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3584976" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ShaniaTwain-BST-Hyde-Park-2024-headliner-news.jpg" alt="仙妮亚·唐恩在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ShaniaTwain-BST-Hyde-Park-2024-headliner-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ShaniaTwain-BST-Hyde-Park-2024-headliner-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ShaniaTwain-BST-Hyde-Park-2024-headliner-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ShaniaTwain-BST-Hyde-Park-2024-headliner-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ShaniaTwain-BST-Hyde-Park-2024-headliner-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-